title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 398-9.2 - Direct deposits

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 398-9.2 - Direct deposits

State Regulations
A confirmed direct deposit of State benefit issuances
will not be replaced with SSP benefits or SSPNA. Notes
